deployment_environment.name: deployment_environment
deployment_environment.queryValue:
SELECT JSONExtractString(labels, 'deployment_environment') AS deployment_environment
FROM signoz_metrics.time_series_v4_1day
WHERE (metric_name = 'signoz_calls_total') AND (unix_milli >= (toUnixTimestamp(now() - toIntervalDay(1)) * 1000))
GROUP BY deployment_environment

service_name.description: The service.name value for the application
service_name.name: service_name
service_name.queryValue:
SELECT JSONExtractString(labels, 'service_name') AS service_name
FROM signoz_metrics.time_series_v4_1day
WHERE (metric_name = 'signoz_calls_total') AND JSONExtractString(labels, 'deployment_environment') = {{.deployment_environment}} AND (unix_milli >= (toUnixTimestamp(now() - toIntervalDay(1)) * 1000))
GROUP BY service_name

top_level_operation.description: The primary operations for the service are defined here. In a web API service, these are the API endpoints. For services that function as consumers, producers, or clients, these are the names of the entry-point spans.
top_level_operation.name: top_level_operation
top_level_operation.queryValue: SELECT name FROM signoz_traces.top_level_operations WHERE serviceName = {{.service_name}} GROUP BY name
